"{\"uid\": \"si.com-college-utah-other-sports-2024-paris-summer-olympics-how-to-watch-former-utah-utes\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The 2024 Paris Summer Olympics will feature six notable\\u00c2\\u00a0women tied to the University of Utah.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 94, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This group includes five athletes and one coach, each bringing their unique talents and stories to the global stage.\", \"from\": 95, \"to\": 211, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's how to watch the former Utes in the games.\\u00c2  The XXXIII Olympiad opening ceremony are just a matter of days away on Friday, July 26.\", \"from\": 212, \"to\": 351, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This marks the starts of the multi-sport event, running until the closing ceremony on Sunday, August 11.\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 456, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Games will be the first held in Europe since London hosted in 2012.\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 528, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 506, \"end\": 512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999998794342063, \"rank\": 9.994032059386421e-08, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every event will be covered onPeacock, EuroSport, and Discovery+ apps.\", \"from\": 529, \"to\": 599, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 568, \"end\": 577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurosport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"EuroSport\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurosport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurosport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Check your local listings for times.\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 636, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A total of 10,500 athletes, representing 206 countries including, approximately 120 heads of states, sovereigns and heads of government are expected to attend.\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 797, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Plouffe, a former standout at Utah, will compete in the event for the Canadian\\u00c2\\u00a0national team.\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 893, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 829, \"end\": 833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_Utes_football\", \"score\": 0.914414185324291, \"rank\": 0.09204749055428307, \"text\": \"Utah\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_Utes_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_Utes_football\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She's one of the top players globally and makes her third Olympic appearance, having previously played in the 2012 and 2016 Olympics with Canada\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s regular\\u00c2\\u00a0team.\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 1057, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She will transition with\\u00c2\\u00a0Crozon, who played for Utah from 2012-2017 and is making her Olympic debut.\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1159, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1084, \"end\": 1090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crozon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Crozon\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crozon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crozon\"}, {\"begin\": 1107, \"end\": 1111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_Utes_football\", \"score\": 0.914414185324291, \"rank\": 0.09204749055428307, \"text\": \"Utah\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_Utes_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_Utes_football\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has been a part of the Canadian 3x3 team since 2019 and played a crucial role in their Olympic qualification.\\u00c2  Crozon and Plouffe previously secured a silver medal at the 2022 FIBA 3x3 World Cup.\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1360, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1187, \"end\": 1195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9999593992008665, \"rank\"