erred to Utah from BYU before signing with Nike and turning pro.\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1750, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1695, \"end\": 1699, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_Utes_football\", \"score\": 0.914414185324291, \"rank\": 0.09204749055428307, \"text\": \"Utah\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_Utes_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_Utes_football\"}, {\"begin\": 1705, \"end\": 1708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BYU_Cougars\", \"score\": 0.9998597664809501, \"rank\": 0.0001153683196737944, \"text\": \"BYU\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BYU_Cougars\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BYU_Cougars\"}, {\"begin\": 1729, \"end\": 1733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Nike\", \"score\": 0.7621796903314266, \"rank\": 0.31133626931532593, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Nike\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Project_Nike\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 23-year-old will compete in the women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 1,500 meters for Canada.\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1821, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1814, \"end\": 1820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.6758157584828538, \"rank\": 0.40841559541655226, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She qualified for the Olympics by placing third at the Canadian Track and Field trials.\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1909, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1877, \"end\": 1885, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9999593992008665, \"rank\": 4.053365301539682e-05, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.